        "name": "make_post",
        "args": {
            "prompt": "Create a visually engaging image featuring Apple’s Vision Pro mixed-reality headset, highlighting its revolutionary spatial computing experience and game-changing potential in technology. Imagine an environment where the mixed-reality comes alive, hinting at the future of immersive tech.",
            "text": "Apple Vision Pro: Revolutionizing Reality\n- Experience immersive computing\n- Cutting-edge mixed-reality tech\n- Step into the future with Apple",
            "name": "apple_vision_pro_post.jpg"
        }
    },
    "thoughts": {
        "text": "Crafting a prompt for the Instagram post with the intention to create a visually engaging image that represents the revolutionary features of Apple’s Vision Pro mixed-reality headset.",
        "reasoning": "This prompt is designed to generate an image for the post that conveys the transformative innovation of the Vision Pro headset. The text for the post is a summarization in bullet point format, encapsulating the key features in a concise manner suitable for Instagram.",
